snippet.title: Noita trailer - PC Gaming Show 2018
snippet.description:
Check out the splashy physics pixels in this sophisticated roguelike. When every pixel is simulated, things can go horribly wrong in spectacular fashion.

See more on http://www.pcgamer.com and watch the PC Gaming Show livestream at https://www.pcgamer.com/pc-gaming-show-2018-watch/
